name: Qatar A380 at 38,000ft
description:
Was flying across Australia yesterday on a Qatar A350 when I spotted its big brother the A380 flying just below us.  

I was on QR914 from Doha to Adelaide on the A350 at about 41,000 feet. 

The other aircraft is QR908 from Doha to Sydney - an A380 flying at  about 38,000 feet.

Too cool not to share straight away - my flight review of the Qatar A350 business class will be up in a few weeks - will add link in here when it's up.  

Happy Travels

Dennis
